            <title>[LU-6735] select appropriate optimization options for ko2iblnd according IB cards installed on the system</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6735</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In order to support different IB cards in the best way we need to have ability to select appropriate optimization options for ko2iblnd according IB cards installed on the system.&lt;/p&gt;

